                    "body": "I second that issue (I just ran into that strange behaviour of Zend_Form). I would also file it as a bug instead of a simple improvement.\n\nTo complete Jaka Jancar's fix, I would also add a loop to check for sub forms :{{code}}\nforeach ($this->getSubForms() as $key => $subForm) {\n                if ($subForm->isErrors()) {\n                    $errors = true;\n                    break;\n                }\n            }\n{{code}}",
